            "title": "半日收市︱全程潛水 恒指半日跌65點報22911點 ATM拖低大市 小米、中芯續破頂",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股經過昨天在二萬三關口得而復失，今早持續調整；重磅科股個別發展，「ATM」全線回吐，小米(01810)與中芯(00981)卻續創新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開199點後初段進一步尋底，跌幅曾擴大至327點，低見22649點，其後迅速由谷底反彈，中段跌幅一度收窄至僅跌1點，衝上22975點，只是暫欠再彈動力，早市後段再度反覆下調；恒指中午收報22911點，跌65點或0.28%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20