y\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02319-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">蒙牛乳業2024年度中期報告封面</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/866x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">華虹半導體官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：美團官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"蒙牛乳業2024年度中期報告封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02319-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">蒙牛乳業2024年度中期報告封面</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數繼續跑贏大市，開市後約45分鐘已開始倒升，後段呈好淡爭持，半日升20點或0.37%，報5659點；國企指數則跌18點或0.22%，報8456點。主板半日成交1518.58億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌57點，報22939點，高水27點。科指期貨升6點，報5662點，高水2點。國指期貨跌18點，報8464點，高水7點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩大強勢股小米與中芯今早又再破頂，小米獲多家券商唱好或上調目標價，股價今早先跌後回升，一度衝上49.5元再創歷史新高，漲2.27%；中午收報48.95元，升幅收窄至1.14%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">繼早前中信里昂將小米目標價升至56.5元後，美銀、星展、華興資本、華泰證券與大華繼顯也上調對該股的目標價，其中美銀與星展對小米新目標均為52元，華泰證券更樂觀，新目標達55.1元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">花旗則從中國智能手機出貨量增長的角度著眼，料內地今年智能手機出貨量升5%至6%，供應鏈內最看好小米、舜宇光學(02382)及瑞聲科技(02018)。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/866x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/866x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">舜宇光學與瑞聲科技今早均跑贏大市，舜宇光學漲4.12%，報89.65元，在藍籌升幅榜上排第4位；瑞聲科技也升3.08%，報48.55元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於中芯，則在美國總統特朗普表示或對進口汽車、晶片和藥物徵收約25%的關稅，並最快在4月2日宣布的消息出台下，與其他在港上市芯片及半導體相關股齊齊逆市造好。中芯最高見51.9元，漲8.58%；中午收報50.85元，仍升6.38%，是表現次佳的藍籌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一主要芯片股華虹半導體(01347)升勢更凌厲，創52周新高，曾衝上37.15元，飆19.26%；中午收報36.65元，漲17.66%，半日成交額達35.08億元，躋身主板股份成交額前10名之列。上海復旦(01385)也升8.62%，報19.92元；中電華大科技(00085)升5.07%，報1.45元；英諾賽科(02577)升3.21%，報56.3元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華虹半導體官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同受美國關稅威脅的車企，今早亦普遍上升。比亞迪(01211)董事長王傳福揚言中國新能源汽車產品及技術領先約3至5年，該股今早再升0.88%，報368.8元；吉利汽車(00175)升0.79%，報17.9元。小鵬汽車(09868)更漲5.41%，報72.05元；理想汽車(02015)升3.7%，報106.6元；蔚來(09866)則在「蔚小理」當中斯人獨憔悴，跌0.99%，報35.15元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今早也有不少大型科股回吐，「ATM」均全程報跌，騰訊(00700)跌0.93%，報498.8元；阿里巴巴(09988)跌1.19%，報124.8元；美團(03690)跌3.07%，報167.6元。單計這3隻股份，已合共拖低恒指近95點。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天收市後派勝市場預期業績的百度(09888)，今早亦受壓，半日跌2.77%，報87.7元。今日中午派成績表的滙控(00005)，今早再創3年新高後倒跌，半日跌0.29%，報86.95元；同系恒生銀行(00011)亦跌0.48%，報104.1元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">異動股方面，人形機器人股優必選(09880)今早曾再觸及100元，漲15.34%；中午收報97.7元，仍升12.69%，半日成交19.81億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"蒙牛乳業2024年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02319-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"蒙牛乳業2024年度中期報告封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02319-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">蒙牛乳業2024年度中期報告封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蒙牛乳業(02319)發盈警後今早股價不跌反升，該公司在通告中亦表明，去年盈利大幅倒退主要受減值等非現金項目影響，剔除減值的利潤與經營現金流按年比較仍然穩健，考慮股息派發時也會剔除減值。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股今早最高報17.48元，升11.76%；中午收報17.3元，仍漲10.61%，穩佔藍籌升幅榜首，半日成交11.32億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14717022-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%85%a8%e7%a8%8b%e6%bd%9b%e6%b0%b4-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c65%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b122911%e9%bb%9e-atm%e6%8b%96%e4%bd%8e%e5%a4%a7",
