            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 11:35:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "遠洋集團境外債務重組計畫獲香港法院批准",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">媒體報道，遠洋集團(03377)境外債務重組計畫，已於今早召開的香港協議安排批准聆訊中，獲香港法院批准。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14716821-%e9%81%a0%e6%b4%8b%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%98%e5%a2%83%e5%a4%96%e5%82%b5%e5%8b%99%e9%87%8d%e7%b5%84%e8%a8%88%e7%95%ab%e7%8d%b2%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e6%b3%95%e9%99%a2%e6%89%b9%e5%87%86",
